query:
SELECT 
            u.id, 
            u.name, 
            u.username,
            COALESCE(NULLIF(ARRAY_AGG((o.id, o.name)), '{NULL}'), '{}') AS "owners!: Vec<Owner>" 
          FROM users u, project_owners o
          WHERE o.deleted_at is NULL
            AND u.id = $1
          GROUP BY u.id
